      { "name": "battery_module_a", "mass_kg": 9.000, "inertia": [4.0e-2, 4.0e-2, 2.0e-2, 0, 0, 0], "geometry_ref": { "type": "mesh_hash", "hash": "free_humanoid_wheeled_battery_module_v0" }, "_metadata": { "comment": "1 kWh hot-swap module, left side, mounted between drive wheels for low COM. Phase 1 spec: 24V 50Ah / 1.2 kWh AGV-class Li-ion pack (e.g. Bioenno BLF-2450A or RoyPow S2450 class) — descriptor still nominally 2 kWh @ 48V via dual modules; Phase 2 picks final cell chemistry, bus voltage, BMS. Vendor: Bioenno Power / RoyPow. Corpus citation: hyundai-boston-dynamics-spot, spot-fuel-cell hot-swap precedent; tesla-optimus / apptronik-apollo / unitree-h1 large-pack precedent." } },
